    <!-- Visualization & Content Choices: 1. Daily Input (HTML Form): Goal=Collect, Interaction=Submit, Justification=Simulates core user action. 2. Automation Flow (HTML/CSS Diagram): Goal=Explain, Interaction=JS-driven animation on submit, Justification=Visually clarifies the product's process. 3. Generated Report (Dynamic Text Block): Goal=Inform, Interaction=JS updates content, Justification=Shows the end result. 4. Team Analytics (Chart.js Donuts/Bars): Goal=Analyze, Interaction=Static data display, Justification=Demonstrates long-term value. Library: Chart.js for Canvas charts. -->
    <!-- CONFIRMATION: NO SVG graphics used. NO Mermaid JS used. -->
